          <title>BP stages from [<xref rid="pone.0268934.ref009" ref-type="bibr">9</xref>] with (optional) low and crisis categories.</title>
          <p>ISH refers to Isolated Systolic Hypertension, IDH refers to Isolated Diastolic Hypertension.</p>
        </caption>
        <alternatives>
          <graphic xlink:href="pone.0268934.t002" id="pone.0268934.t002g" position="float"/>
          <table frame="box" rules="all" border="0">
